### 8. Mobile & Responsive

**Responsive Layout**
- Layout adapts to screen size
- Content prioritized on small screens
- Touch targets adequate (min 44x44px)
- No horizontal scrolling required
- Tables responsive or scrollable

**Touch Interaction**
- No hover-only interactions
